latestIgtvVideos.title: My air purifier from @trusens_in
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I have been using the @trusens_in air purifier for 2 months now and I must tell u, it’s helped me in a big way! 
Since I am an asthma patient, even a little bit of dust in the air would trigger my breathing pattern and with the virus scare I was even note in the end to find something that helps me purify my home. 
 
And then I came across this -
It has 4 levels of purification which includes UV sterilization that kills germs and bacteria, a remote SensorPod that communicates to the purifier to adjust the fan speed as needed and also a color-coded LED Air Quality Display that tells me the air quality level in my home!
 
The best part is it has a special pet filter so the possibility of my pets carrying dust and also just their hair in general affecting my health could be eradicated made me want to know more about the brand. 
 
The specialty filters are newly launched by TruSens to help combat specific issues, such as pet dander and hair & odors and VOCs. The one I’m using is the Pet Filter with True HEPA which helps to capture up to 99.97% of pet dander and hair, and helps eliminate common pet odors! If you’re always cooking and using strong chemicals to clean your home, get the Odor Filter as it helps to eliminate cooking and cleaning odors and reduce VOCs!
 
So I tried @trusens_in and the rest is history! I’m using the Z-2000 Air Purifier with Pet Filter.
 
@trusens_in is running a Diwali sale on Amazon with over 50% discounts! Sale ends on 13 Nov so hurry! Shop now: http://bit.ly/trusensairpurifiers
 
P/S: Specialty filters are sold separately and can only be used with TruSens air purifiers. The purifier comes with the standard 4-in-1 filters and UV Bulb.
